gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bulls 116, Raptors 110
gameRecap.excerpt: The Bulls defeated the Raptors, 116-110. Nikola Vucevic recorded 24 points, 13 rebounds, and seven assists for the Bulls, with DeMar DeRozan (24 points, seven rebounds) and Coby White (23 points, eight rebounds) combining for 47 points in the victory. Scottie Barnes tallied 31 points, seven rebounds, and six assists for the Raptors in the losing effort. The Bulls improve to 20-23, while the Raptors fall to 16-26.
